WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.263
<i>It happened again!</i>

00:00:03.057 --> 00:00:05.143
<i>I blacked out again.</i>

00:00:09.981 --> 00:00:11.774
<i>How many times was that?</i>

00:00:12.150 --> 00:00:16.612
<i>I black out amid battle,
again and again...</i>

00:00:16.612 --> 00:00:18.906
<i>only to find myself
back where I left off.</i>

00:00:27.624 --> 00:00:29.209
<i>This brings back memories.</i>

00:00:29.917 --> 00:00:31.462
<i>I always enjoy my battles,</i>

00:00:31.962 --> 00:00:34.048
<i>but not to the point
where I'd lose myself</i>

00:00:34.048 --> 00:00:36.091
<i>or have blackouts
in the middle of it.</i>

00:00:37.009 --> 00:00:39.011
<i>That happened only once...</i>

00:00:40.344 --> 00:00:43.432
<i>That day I fought you.</i>

00:01:04.203 --> 00:01:08.956
<i>The blue skies above are hopelessly clear</i>

00:01:09.082 --> 00:01:14.171
<i>At my wit's end, I feel a growing frustration</i>

00:01:14.587 --> 00:01:19.009
<i>As if to laugh at us hopeless cowards</i>

00:01:19.343 --> 00:01:22.763
<i>Countless eyes stare at us</i>

00:01:23.221 --> 00:01:29.102
<i>This soul of mine breaks again and again</i>

00:01:29.394 --> 00:01:32.272
<i>All I can do is hold it tight</i>

00:01:33.481 --> 00:01:38.528
<i>Until the day it turns to ash</i>

00:01:38.778 --> 00:01:41.406
<i>I've absorbed all of this sorrow</i>

00:01:41.531 --> 00:01:46.036
<i>It has shaped me, painted me</i>

00:01:46.161 --> 00:01:48.871
<i>But that's how we got here, right?</i>

00:01:48.996 --> 00:01:53.835
<i>One step at a time, just like breathing</i>

00:01:53.960 --> 00:01:56.462
<i>These countless scars on my palm</i>

00:01:56.587 --> 00:01:58.465
<i>That no longer fade</i>

00:01:58.590 --> 00:02:02.218
<i>Are my badge, my story</i>

00:02:02.510 --> 00:02:06.181
<i>I faced the fear and shred it to pieces</i>

00:02:06.306 --> 00:02:09.268
<i>And let it walk beside me once more</i>

00:02:09.268 --> 00:02:13.938
BLEACH: THOUSAND-YEAR BLOOD WAR

00:02:33.584 --> 00:02:37.670
RUKON DISTRICT -
SEVERAL HUNDRED YEARS AGO
Captain!

00:02:38.129 --> 00:02:39.173
It's just not possible...

00:02:39.590 --> 00:02:41.300
No matter how much we search
the Rukon District...

00:02:41.800 --> 00:02:45.012
I doubt we'll find anyone
strong enough to satisfy you.

00:02:47.014 --> 00:02:48.848
I'm impressed you figured out
my true intent...

00:02:49.765 --> 00:02:52.269
Cutting down gangs from
the Rukon District won't

00:02:52.269 --> 00:02:54.896
make much difference in preserving
the peace in the Seireitei.

00:02:55.813 --> 00:03:00.818
The size of this pile of bodies is
the size of your dissatisfaction!

00:03:02.236 --> 00:03:03.405
That pile...

00:03:03.906 --> 00:03:05.574
How long has it been there?

00:03:05.949 --> 00:03:08.701
Huh?
This wasn't your doing?

00:03:14.040 --> 00:03:15.792
Who's that kid?

00:03:18.836 --> 00:03:19.795
<i>I was bored...</i>

00:03:20.963 --> 00:03:22.549
<i>With the sword.
With fighting.</i>

00:03:23.383 --> 00:03:27.221
<i>And so I wandered around
in search of a foe</i>

00:03:27.221 --> 00:03:29.097
<i>who could please my sword.</i>

00:03:30.598 --> 00:03:34.853
<i>That's probably why our swords
drew us two weary souls together.</i>

00:03:36.062 --> 00:03:37.063
<i>Such bliss...</i>

00:03:38.481 --> 00:03:39.983
<i>I hadn't expected this.</i>

00:03:40.442 --> 00:03:41.818
<i>I never would have thought that</i>

00:03:41.818 --> 00:03:43.986
<i>I could experience
such unparalleled joy</i>

00:03:43.986 --> 00:03:46.615
<i>by crossing blades with a child...</i>

00:03:47.657 --> 00:03:49.492
<i>But I never thought</i>

00:03:49.492 --> 00:03:54.163
<i>that child would place shackles
on himself because of our battle.</i>

00:03:58.961 --> 00:03:59.961
<i>I landed one!</i>

00:04:00.378 --> 00:04:04.048
<i>Before, I could only react.
But now, I can counter it.</i>

00:04:04.548 --> 00:04:06.927
<i>It's almost as if each time
I experience a blackout...</i>

00:04:06.927 --> 00:04:09.012
<i>I wake up feeling reborn!</i>

00:04:09.887 --> 00:04:13.975
<i>Kenpachi Zaraki, you probably
have not realized this...</i>

00:04:14.309 --> 00:04:16.310
<i>That you are unconsciously</i>

00:04:16.310 --> 00:04:21.399
<i>restraining your powers
while in battle.</i>

00:04:22.733 --> 00:04:27.906
<i>Do you know why you narrowly lost
your battle with Ichigo Kurosaki?</i>

00:04:29.199 --> 00:04:34.245
<i>Do you know why you narrowly won
your battle with Nnoitora Gilga?</i>

00:04:35.747 --> 00:04:37.165
<i>Was it because they were strong...?</i>

00:04:37.958 --> 00:04:39.875
<i>I'm sure that's how it seemed
to the others.</i>

00:04:40.836 --> 00:04:43.379
<i>But I knew that wasn't the case.</i>

00:04:44.964 --> 00:04:50.470
<i>In each instance, you suppressed
your power to the limit.</i>

00:04:52.596 --> 00:04:57.226
<i>During that battle, we both
experienced unparalleled joy.</i>

00:04:58.353 --> 00:05:00.021
<i>The only difference was that</i>

00:05:00.021 --> 00:05:05.360
<i>you learned the joy
of fighting on the edge.</i>

00:05:06.069 --> 00:05:08.487
<i>That is my sin.</i>

00:05:09.406 --> 00:05:11.074
<i>You must have been ecstatic.</i>

00:05:11.574 --> 00:05:13.242
<i>Everyone around you was weak.</i>

00:05:13.869 --> 00:05:15.829
<i>You had no enemies
you could test your sword against.</i>

00:05:16.495 --> 00:05:22.627
<i>I was the first foe you encountered
who could rival your power.</i>

00:05:23.711 --> 00:05:24.670
<i>However...</i>

00:05:25.838 --> 00:05:27.966
<i>I was weaker than you.</i>

00:05:29.009 --> 00:05:31.595
<i>I was the first person in your life
you could call a foe.</i>

00:05:32.137 --> 00:05:34.014
<i>You believed that if you lost me,</i>

00:05:34.014 --> 00:05:37.559
<i>you would never experience
the joy of battle ever again...</i>

00:05:37.975 --> 00:05:39.853
<i>You wanted to bring yourself
down to my level,</i>

00:05:40.603 --> 00:05:42.646
<i>so little by little,
you unconsciously</i>

00:05:43.189 --> 00:05:49.403
<i>began to suppress your power
into a deep, dark place.</i>

00:05:50.322 --> 00:05:51.865
<i>I was devastated.</i>

00:05:52.656 --> 00:05:56.495
<i>My weakness drove you
to suppress your power.</i>

00:05:57.579 --> 00:06:00.040
<i>But one day, I noticed something.</i>

00:06:00.581 --> 00:06:04.502
<i>Each time you flirt with death
against a powerful foe,</i>

00:06:04.752 --> 00:06:07.004
<i>you start to break your shackles</i>

00:06:07.004 --> 00:06:09.382
<i>and return to the person
you used to be...</i>

00:06:12.259 --> 00:06:13.387
<i>I am strong.</i>

00:06:13.762 --> 00:06:15.346
<i>Stronger than anyone besides you.</i>

00:06:16.264 --> 00:06:19.225
<i>That is why I will kill you.</i>

00:06:20.310 --> 00:06:22.269
<i>Even if it takes a hundred
or a thousand tries.</i>

00:06:23.230 --> 00:06:26.233
<i>That is why I will heal you.</i>

00:06:26.942 --> 00:06:28.819
<i>Again and again...</i>

00:06:29.944 --> 00:06:33.322
<i>Until you return
to what you really are.</i>

00:06:35.408 --> 00:06:36.410
<i>From there...</i>

00:06:36.660 --> 00:06:38.954
<i>you will surpass me
and reach even greater heights...</i>

00:06:39.579 --> 00:06:40.579
<i>Do it!</i>

00:06:49.047 --> 00:06:51.507
You thought I was dead, didn't you?

00:06:52.884 --> 00:06:53.884
Guess again.

00:06:54.845 --> 00:07:01.685
You, of all people, should know
the reason why I mastered Kaido.

00:07:05.355 --> 00:07:06.689
Bankai...

00:07:11.819 --> 00:07:13.362
Minazuki.

00:07:20.995 --> 00:07:23.874
Playtime is over...

00:08:02.870 --> 00:08:04.831
<i>Ah, I'm melting...</i>

00:08:11.086 --> 00:08:12.838
<i>I'm melting away...</i>

00:08:24.643 --> 00:08:25.976
<i>This is fun.</i>

00:08:26.561 --> 00:08:27.937
<i>What is this?</i>

00:08:30.731 --> 00:08:31.732
<i>It's different.</i>

00:08:32.024 --> 00:08:33.235
<i>All of it.</i>

00:08:33.735 --> 00:08:35.736
<i>Everything feels different.</i>

00:08:36.654 --> 00:08:37.655
<i>But why?</i>

00:08:40.366 --> 00:08:41.534
<i>So that's it...</i>

00:08:48.457 --> 00:08:51.293
<i>I've been asleep this whole time.</i>

00:08:51.919 --> 00:08:58.592
<i>I've been playing out our exchange
in my dreams.</i>

00:08:59.552 --> 00:09:03.097
<i>All this time, I thought there
wasn't a word for this exchange.</i>

00:09:03.847 --> 00:09:09.604
<i>But thanks to you, I've finally
learned what it's called.</i>

00:09:10.647 --> 00:09:11.730
<i>Thank you.</i>

00:09:11.981 --> 00:09:12.982
<i>So this...</i>

00:09:13.817 --> 00:09:15.192
<i>This is...!</i>

00:09:15.985 --> 00:09:18.572
<i>This is battle!</i>

00:09:19.530 --> 00:09:21.825
<i>Hey, did you know?</i>

00:09:22.491 --> 00:09:25.035
<i>I love fighting.
I love it.</i>

00:09:25.452 --> 00:09:28.248
<i>There's nothing I can do about it.</i>

00:09:28.706 --> 00:09:30.500
<i>Yes, I knew.</i>

00:09:30.833 --> 00:09:33.336
<i>Probably long before you ever did.</i>

00:09:34.754 --> 00:09:36.130
<i>Say, Kenpachi Zaraki...</i>

00:09:37.131 --> 00:09:39.967
<i>You learned the ability
to suppress yourself</i>

00:09:39.967 --> 00:09:42.511
<i>so you could enjoy the battle
for eternity.</i>

00:09:43.929 --> 00:09:46.725
<i>I learned the ability
to heal myself</i>

00:09:46.725 --> 00:09:49.269
<i>so I could enjoy the battle
for eternity.</i>

00:09:50.352 --> 00:09:53.230
<i>But now, I am certain.</i>

00:09:53.856 --> 00:09:58.861
<i>This power I obtained
was for this single battle.</i>

00:10:00.488 --> 00:10:02.740
<i>In any era,
there can only be one Kenpachi...</i>

00:10:03.325 --> 00:10:06.577
<i>That is the rule
as well as an inevitable fate.</i>

00:10:07.328 --> 00:10:11.332
<i>Because when the strong
find the next strongest,</i>

00:10:11.832 --> 00:10:15.169
<i>they can no longer swing
their sword for their own sake.</i>

00:10:15.879 --> 00:10:18.923
<i>The tip of their sword
will always be pointed</i>

00:10:18.923 --> 00:10:21.259
<i>either toward
killing the next strongest...</i>

00:10:22.009 --> 00:10:24.553
<i>or toward nurturing them.</i>

00:10:25.721 --> 00:10:26.931
<i>The tip of my sword is...</i>

00:10:36.732 --> 00:10:37.734
<i>He's the one.</i>

00:10:38.192 --> 00:10:41.488
<i>This child is the one to be worthy
of the name Kenpachi.</i>

00:10:44.990 --> 00:10:46.076
<i>Farewell...</i>

00:10:46.868 --> 00:10:48.620
<i>The one man in this world...</i>

00:10:51.373 --> 00:10:53.500
<i>who brought me joy.</i>

00:10:57.586 --> 00:11:00.715
That was magnificent,
Kenpachi Zaraki.

00:11:02.509 --> 00:11:04.052
And now, this battle is over...

00:11:09.224 --> 00:11:10.432
It's over?

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:14.104
Wait, are you going to die?

00:11:15.230 --> 00:11:16.898
No, don't die.

00:11:17.899 --> 00:11:18.899
Not yet.

00:11:19.024 --> 00:11:20.735
I still haven't had enough.

00:11:22.028 --> 00:11:24.114
Please don't die.

00:11:25.280 --> 00:11:26.408
I'm begging you...

00:11:27.866 --> 00:11:30.828
Don't die!

00:11:32.746 --> 00:11:33.914
<i>He's like a child.</i>

00:11:34.832 --> 00:11:37.251
<i>What is there to cry about?</i>

00:11:38.293 --> 00:11:42.131
<i>Sure, now that you've regained
your strength and defeated me...</i>

00:11:42.923 --> 00:11:45.759
<i>You might see yourself
returning to the days</i>

00:11:45.759 --> 00:11:48.846
<i>when you find many of your battles
to be boring.</i>

00:11:49.764 --> 00:11:51.599
<i>But right now,</i>

00:11:51.599 --> 00:11:53.726
<i>you have foes you can fight
to your heart's content...</i>

00:11:54.394 --> 00:11:56.730
<i>and comrades you can
cross swords with on equal terms.</i>

00:11:57.522 --> 00:12:03.360
<i>Most of all, you have a partner
who has awakened alongside you.</i>

00:12:05.989 --> 00:12:11.160
<i>Everything I have gained until now,
I've relinquished to you.</i>

00:12:12.245 --> 00:12:15.123
<i>I no longer possess anything.</i>

00:12:16.124 --> 00:12:19.961
<i>Even the name of Kenpachi, which
I couldn't give to you back then,</i>

00:12:20.461 --> 00:12:22.922
<i>has finally vanished from my hands.</i>

00:12:24.215 --> 00:12:26.967
<i>Rejoice, Kenpachi Zaraki...</i>

00:12:28.470 --> 00:12:30.429
<i>Rejoice for me as I pass away.</i>

00:12:32.056 --> 00:12:39.605
<i>Ah, what sheer bliss to die from
accomplishing one's purpose...</i>

00:12:55.746 --> 00:12:56.831
<i>Kenpachi...</i>

00:12:57.624 --> 00:12:59.082
<i>Kenpachi of Zaraki...</i>

00:12:59.667 --> 00:13:00.668
Who's there?

00:13:00.835 --> 00:13:02.211
Who's calling my name?!

00:13:02.836 --> 00:13:03.962
Show yourself!

00:13:04.880 --> 00:13:08.592
<i>It seems my voice
has finally reached you.</i>

00:13:10.803 --> 00:13:12.806
<i>The voice of the one</i>

00:13:13.722 --> 00:13:17.351
<i>who has been watching you
longer and closer than anyone.</i>

00:13:20.562 --> 00:13:22.816
Huh?
Who the hell are you?

00:13:24.525 --> 00:13:25.527
Kenpachi...

00:13:26.235 --> 00:13:27.861
Kenpachi of Zaraki!

00:13:28.904 --> 00:13:31.865
<i>It's nice to meet you,
Kenpachi Zaraki.</i>

00:13:33.158 --> 00:13:34.660
<i>My name is...</i>

00:13:50.634 --> 00:13:53.263
HOOHDEN - LANDING AREA

00:13:55.097 --> 00:13:56.432
There's nobody here.

00:14:00.769 --> 00:14:02.230
What is that noise?!

00:14:02.938 --> 00:14:04.774
<i>Lower your heads, lower your heads!</i>

00:14:04.774 --> 00:14:05.942
<i>Because...</i>

00:14:06.484 --> 00:14:08.735
<i>Your heads are so high!</i>

00:14:10.238 --> 00:14:13.658
<i>I am the number one
Zanpakuto creator!</i>

00:14:13.783 --> 00:14:15.576
<i>Oh-Etsu Nimaiya!</i>

00:14:15.743 --> 00:14:17.245
<i>S-I-K-U...</i>

00:14:17.245 --> 00:14:19.205
<i>Y-O-R-O!</i>

00:14:19.205 --> 00:14:21.624
<i>Sikuyoro, whazzup!</i>

00:14:22.000 --> 00:14:25.003
<i>Zanpakuto...!</i>

00:14:25.003 --> 00:14:26.086
<i>Love it!</i>

00:14:26.629 --> 00:14:30.133
"GALAXY HOOHDEN"
- Welcome!
- Welcome!

00:14:34.596 --> 00:14:36.096
What the hell is all this?

00:14:36.264 --> 00:14:38.682
Paradise!
Paradise!

00:14:38.682 --> 00:14:40.018
Don't be fooled...

00:14:40.559 --> 00:14:41.936
They're probably

00:14:41.936 --> 00:14:44.438
- illusions or something.
- This is truly paradise!

00:14:44.438 --> 00:14:45.565
Shut up...!

00:14:45.565 --> 00:14:48.692
So, Kurosaki!
Abarai!

00:14:48.692 --> 00:14:50.736
And that strange
stuffed animal, too!

00:14:51.028 --> 00:14:54.698
Did you guys enjoy
my welcoming show?!

00:14:54.823 --> 00:15:00.538
Once again, I am Oh-Etsu Nimaiya,
the master of this Hoohden!

00:15:00.538 --> 00:15:02.581
"BLADE GOD" - OH-ETSU NIMAIYA

00:15:02.581 --> 00:15:04.375
<i>Sikuyoro</i>, whazzup!

00:15:05.626 --> 00:15:07.253
Uh, uh!
Pow, pow, pow!

00:15:07.253 --> 00:15:08.337
Hey!

00:15:08.671 --> 00:15:10.214
Trade places with me...

00:15:10.798 --> 00:15:13.301
I can't keep up
with this guy's vibe.

00:15:13.551 --> 00:15:16.346
You idiot!
I can't keep up with it, either!

00:15:16.678 --> 00:15:17.679
Hmm...

00:15:17.679 --> 00:15:19.432
Something's not right...

00:15:19.765 --> 00:15:22.393
You guys aren't any fun!

00:15:23.394 --> 00:15:23.977
Want to leave?

00:15:23.977 --> 00:15:25.062
- Huh?!
- Huh?!

00:15:27.606 --> 00:15:29.817
- No, we'd like to stay, sir!
- Please let us stay, sir!

00:15:30.652 --> 00:15:32.570
No!
No, no, no!

00:15:32.570 --> 00:15:35.615
That's not the right way to ask!

00:15:35.615 --> 00:15:38.408
The formal way you do it
in Hoohden is... like this!

00:15:39.785 --> 00:15:40.787
Please, sir!

00:15:40.787 --> 00:15:42.245
I'm not doing that pose!

00:15:42.788 --> 00:15:44.081
Calm down, Ichigo!

00:15:44.374 --> 00:15:45.375
We've got to do it!

00:15:46.583 --> 00:15:47.585
Damn it...

00:15:49.586 --> 00:15:50.754
- Please, sir!
- Please, sir!

00:15:50.754 --> 00:15:52.090
Nice pose!

00:15:52.798 --> 00:15:54.591
- Take a look, my honeys!
- Oh my god, that's hilarious!

00:15:54.591 --> 00:15:56.177
- Take a look, my honeys!
- They look like bananas!

00:15:56.635 --> 00:15:57.720
<i>- Bastard...
- Bastard...</i>

00:15:58.804 --> 00:15:59.806
How long are you...

00:16:00.514 --> 00:16:02.517
going to be doing that?!

00:16:02.975 --> 00:16:04.811
What was that for, Mera?!

00:16:07.813 --> 00:16:08.815
Follow me!

00:16:12.735 --> 00:16:15.446
"HOOHDEN"
<i>This</i> is the real Hoohden!

00:16:15.446 --> 00:16:16.279
"HOOHDEN"

00:16:16.697 --> 00:16:17.823
I don't know what to say...

00:16:18.198 --> 00:16:19.283
Come on in!

00:16:19.741 --> 00:16:22.202
I don't want to go into
such a depressing place!

00:16:22.327 --> 00:16:23.955
I wanna go back
to that other place!

00:16:23.955 --> 00:16:26.541
I agree with you,
strange stuffed animal!

00:16:26.541 --> 00:16:29.376
You feel me, right?!

00:16:34.006 --> 00:16:35.048
That hurt...

00:16:35.048 --> 00:16:36.926
Hey!
What the hell is this?!

00:16:37.427 --> 00:16:40.178
Kurosaki, Abarai, have you noticed?

00:16:40.388 --> 00:16:43.599
You two have not met
a single Soul Reaper besides me

00:16:43.599 --> 00:16:45.600
on your way here.

00:16:47.602 --> 00:16:50.272
All of my honeys
you saw earlier are...

00:16:50.981 --> 00:16:52.275
Zanpakuto.

00:16:52.775 --> 00:16:53.859
Zanpakuto?!

00:16:54.609 --> 00:16:56.738
What's this?
That's odd.

00:16:56.738 --> 00:16:57.989
Very odd indeed.

00:16:58.155 --> 00:16:59.699
You guys are Soul Reapers

00:16:59.699 --> 00:17:02.910
yet you can't tell the difference
between Soul Reapers and Zanpakuto?

00:17:03.411 --> 00:17:05.246
What is wrong with you guys?!

00:17:05.496 --> 00:17:08.583
Is it because you're both
the sort of unloving souls

00:17:08.583 --> 00:17:11.711
who would allow <i>this</i>
to happen to your Zanpakuto?

00:17:12.545 --> 00:17:13.671
Hey!
When did you—?!

00:17:16.590 --> 00:17:17.633
Oh my...

00:17:17.633 --> 00:17:22.888
A Zanpakuto that doesn't
receive love is so easily broken.

00:17:23.431 --> 00:17:28.478
You two are completely surrounded...
by the anger of Zanpakuto.

00:17:30.395 --> 00:17:32.565
If you can make it
out of there alive,

00:17:32.565 --> 00:17:35.358
I'll consider fixing
your Zanpakuto.

00:17:35.651 --> 00:17:36.652
What?!

00:17:36.778 --> 00:17:38.028
I'll say it one more time!

00:17:38.695 --> 00:17:41.824
I am the number one
Zanpakuto creator!

00:17:42.450 --> 00:17:45.411
Ten, nine, eight, seven, six, five...

00:17:45.411 --> 00:17:46.996
four... three...

00:17:46.996 --> 00:17:49.164
Two, that's me, Oh-Etsu Nimaiya!

00:17:49.499 --> 00:17:51.625
I don't make swords for losers.

00:17:51.625 --> 00:17:52.667
You bastard...

00:17:52.960 --> 00:17:55.505
<i>Sikuyoro</i>, whazzup.

00:17:57.131 --> 00:17:58.508
There's something here...

00:17:58.508 --> 00:17:59.592
Yeah...

00:17:59.592 --> 00:18:01.844
There's nothing to be afraid of.

00:18:02.553 --> 00:18:05.765
They are the ultimate Zanpakuto
that can become anything...

00:18:06.516 --> 00:18:07.808
They're Asauchi.

00:18:09.477 --> 00:18:10.478
Asauchi...?

00:18:10.478 --> 00:18:11.854
ASAUCHI

00:18:12.646 --> 00:18:14.397
It's the nameless Zanpakuto...

00:18:14.690 --> 00:18:17.192
temporarily issued to
the over 6,000 members

00:18:17.192 --> 00:18:20.529
of the Thirteen Court Guard Squads
during their time in the Academy

00:18:20.529 --> 00:18:23.490
and then officially issued
when they become a squad member.

00:18:24.032 --> 00:18:27.577
Every Soul Reaper eats and sleeps
with their Asauchi.

00:18:27.577 --> 00:18:29.329
Through continuous training,

00:18:29.329 --> 00:18:32.959
they imprint the essence
of their soul upon their Asauchi

00:18:32.959 --> 00:18:35.920
to create their personalized
Zanpakuto!

00:18:36.796 --> 00:18:40.215
And the one who creates
all of those Asauchi by himself...

00:18:40.215 --> 00:18:44.261
is me, the Blade God,
Oh-Etsu Nimaiya!

00:18:44.636 --> 00:18:48.432
Why do we have to be attacked
by these Asauchi?!

00:18:48.766 --> 00:18:51.644
There's no need to think about why!

00:18:52.310 --> 00:18:55.940
The important thing to know
is that they're angry with you.

00:18:55.940 --> 00:18:57.023
For what?!

00:18:57.023 --> 00:18:59.818
For the way you use your Zanpakuto.

00:19:00.111 --> 00:19:01.194
The way we use them?!

00:19:01.362 --> 00:19:03.446
You don't understand?
Of course, you don't.

00:19:03.446 --> 00:19:05.365
Is it how you fight,
or how you swing?

00:19:05.365 --> 00:19:07.576
That's not it, so what is it?

00:19:08.326 --> 00:19:10.538
This is how they think of you.

00:19:10.538 --> 00:19:12.248
"We're fundamentally different!"

00:19:12.248 --> 00:19:14.208
Let's start by discussing

00:19:14.208 --> 00:19:17.252
whether Zanpakuto or Soul Reapers
are superior!

00:19:35.229 --> 00:19:38.231
<i>Everything we had left behind</i>

00:19:38.398 --> 00:19:42.528
<i>Our breaths blending as mist</i>

00:19:42.528 --> 00:19:47.032
<i>without form or expression</i>

00:19:47.157 --> 00:19:51.287
<i>We lie buried as we glare
into the distance</i>

00:19:51.621 --> 00:19:54.248
<i>I can't hear anything</i>

00:19:54.373 --> 00:19:57.500
<i>I can't seem to cut anything</i>

00:19:57.626 --> 00:20:00.003
<i>It feels like I'm sinking</i>

00:20:00.128 --> 00:20:01.963
<i>Falling, falling</i>

00:20:01.963 --> 00:20:03.048
<i>Touching</i>

00:20:03.173 --> 00:20:06.551
<i>Eyes struck wide open</i>

00:20:06.551 --> 00:20:09.971
<i>Something no one has ever seen</i>

00:20:10.096 --> 00:20:16.269
<i>The furthest reaches are now visible to us</i>

00:20:16.645 --> 00:20:20.273
<i>It cannot be undone
and cannot be stopped</i>

00:20:20.398 --> 00:20:23.611
<i>This ensuing struggle</i>

00:20:23.818 --> 00:20:28.531
<i>Whisk it away beyond
the ends of the earth</i>

00:20:28.657 --> 00:20:30.701
<i>Along with our breaths</i>

00:20:30.910 --> 00:20:32.161
<i>Take everything</i>

00:20:32.161 --> 00:20:36.915
<i>Whisk it away beyond
the ends of the earth</i>

00:20:37.040 --> 00:20:38.960
<i>Along with our futures</i>

00:20:39.085 --> 00:20:40.836
<i>Along with our world</i>

00:20:41.921 --> 00:20:45.173
<i>Something no one has ever seen</i>

00:20:45.298 --> 00:20:51.555
<i>The furthest reaches are now
visible to us</i>

00:20:51.555 --> 00:20:53.641
<i>Don't you know God's demand?</i>

00:20:53.766 --> 00:20:55.558
<i>Don't you know God's demand?</i>

00:20:55.684 --> 00:20:59.063
<i>As we tear each other down</i>

00:21:03.233 --> 00:21:05.736
71 hours and 48 minutes...

00:21:05.987 --> 00:21:08.530
You lasted for three days.

00:21:08.530 --> 00:21:09.656
I'm impressed.

00:21:10.825 --> 00:21:13.118
You pass, Renji!

00:21:15.746 --> 00:21:20.750
And... you fail, Ichigo!

00:21:21.126 --> 00:21:24.171
W-Wait... I can still...

00:21:24.171 --> 00:21:26.589
Nope! No waiting.
You're done.

00:21:26.589 --> 00:21:28.675
You fail.
The end.

00:21:29.134 --> 00:21:31.679
I...can still keep going!

00:21:32.305 --> 00:21:33.306
Let me do this...!

00:21:33.596 --> 00:21:35.724
There's no time limit, is there?!

00:21:36.142 --> 00:21:38.810
There isn't a time limit,
but rather an emotional limit.

00:21:39.144 --> 00:21:42.731
I'm not talking about whether
you can keep going or not.

00:21:42.940 --> 00:21:46.527
You just weren't chosen
by an Asauchi.

00:21:46.902 --> 00:21:48.320
It's not going to happen.

00:21:48.320 --> 00:21:50.196
It's over.
The end.

00:21:50.196 --> 00:21:52.282
- Wait!
- Give it a rest.

00:21:52.700 --> 00:21:56.453
You were dumped.
So stop whining.

00:21:57.038 --> 00:21:59.414
What's become perfectly clear
in these last three days

00:21:59.414 --> 00:22:03.669
is that Renji's a Soul Reaper
while you, Ichigo, are not.

00:22:04.211 --> 00:22:07.798
Don't worry,
I'll open up a way out of there.

00:22:08.257 --> 00:22:09.258
And so,

00:22:09.924 --> 00:22:11.801
time for you to go home.

00:22:15.765 --> 00:22:16.766
What?

00:22:17.307 --> 00:22:20.185
- Mera! Pull him out of there.
- Sure.

00:22:20.603 --> 00:22:22.063
H-Hold on a second!

00:22:22.313 --> 00:22:23.396
You're joking, right?!

00:22:24.606 --> 00:22:25.607
Oh, one more thing.

00:22:25.607 --> 00:22:28.568
Don't enter the Soul Society
ever again.

00:22:29.236 --> 00:22:31.529
The Soul Society
is the land of Soul Reapers.

00:22:31.529 --> 00:22:34.032
An ordinary human
without a Zanpakuto

00:22:34.032 --> 00:22:35.910
has no right to enter it.

00:22:36.618 --> 00:22:37.619
Damn it...!

00:22:37.787 --> 00:22:41.874
You really think I'm just going
to leave after coming this far?

00:22:42.583 --> 00:22:45.711
If I leave now,
what'll happen to Zangetsu?

00:22:46.170 --> 00:22:48.672
Whether you leave or not,
it makes no difference.

00:22:48.838 --> 00:22:50.840
Zangetsu cannot be fixed anymore.

00:22:50.840 --> 00:22:51.925
Or rather,

00:22:52.093 --> 00:22:53.635
I <i>won't</i> fix him.

00:22:55.179 --> 00:22:56.180
As I said before...

00:22:56.513 --> 00:22:58.641
Ten, nine, eight, seven, six, five...

00:22:58.766 --> 00:22:59.724
four... three...

00:22:59.724 --> 00:23:01.769
Two, that's me, Oh-Etsu Nimaiya!

00:23:01.769 --> 00:23:05.230
I don't make swords
for a fake Soul Reaper.

00:23:06.231 --> 00:23:07.232
You bastard!

00:23:11.945 --> 00:23:14.698
Bye-buh-bye, Ichigo!

00:23:18.743 --> 00:23:21.788
You're no good
as you are now, Ichigo.

00:23:22.163 --> 00:23:25.291
The fact that an Asauchi
didn't choose you...

00:23:25.584 --> 00:23:28.921
The fact that you've fought
this long <i>without</i> an Asauchi...

00:23:28.921 --> 00:23:32.090
You don't understand
the significance of this.

00:23:33.509 --> 00:23:35.803
You need to go back...

00:23:35.803 --> 00:23:37.137
Back to your roots.

00:23:37.596 --> 00:23:41.267
And you must learn
what your roots are.

00:23:45.770 --> 00:23:46.689
Even if you are unable to return
upon learning them.

00:23:46.689 --> 00:23:50.483
"KUROSAKI CLINIC"
Even if you are unable to return
upon learning them.

00:23:56.323 --> 00:24:00.452
<i>"You, without sin,
are like the sun."</i>

